  "title": "Is there a way to display list of XX newest entries, but only up to 2 from each category?",
  "body": "**Do you want to request a *feature* or report a *bug*?**\r\nfeature\r\n\r\n**Bug: What is the current behavior?**\r\ndon't know if exists\r\n\r\n**Bug: What is the expected behavior?**\r\nwant to have an ability to display a widget that would include list of [most recent | any other sort] entries, but with option to include only up to X number of entries from each category\r\n\r\n**Bug: What browsers are impacted? Which versions?**\r\nn/a\r\n\r\n**Feature: What is your use case for such a feature?**\r\necommerce store - New Arrivals, but could easily be applied to any \"Carousel-like\" list of products, where output is limited\r\n",
